Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Get Descriptive and Diagnostic Insights Programmatically

Use Einstein Discovery's Insights API to embed insights from your model into any website or dashboard. The Insights API provides REST API endpoints that enable you to:

* query descriptive and diagnostic insights
* get insight summaries
* get metadata for models and model versions

Each resource (models, model versions, and insights) has a unique id. To interact with the Insights API, use your favorite REST client and have a connected app that handles Salesforce authentication.

Required user permissions: Use Einstein Discovery.

Note: Einstein Discovery stories are now models.
title: Programmatically Accessing Insights with Salesforce Einstein Discovery
